description: Lookin’ to eat something delicious but don’t feel like cookin’? Ditch the stove and head over to The Grove to indulge in their beautiful Banh Mi sandwiches, lovely Loaded Sides, and of course their crazy tasty Kronuts (the beautiful marriage of a croissant and a donut). With a selection of simple flavors including Chocolate, Cinnamon Sugar, and Strawberry, and great gourmet flavors like Strawberry Cheesecake, Cookie Butter, S’mores, and more, and the fact that you can even build your own with a variety of tasty toppings, Houston can’t help but go “whoa” for these Kronuts. You can fill your Banh Mi sandwich with any of these premium meats: 5 Spiced Pork, Lemongrass Chicken, Hawaiian Spam, and Korean Chopped Beef. And you can’t top their Kim Chi Fries or Tots!Come eat at The Grove and enjoy this treasure trove of a green truck.
name: The Grove Donut Truck
